description: RMF area <filereq root base ext> file requester with parent dir and ext output
---

Similar to `filebox`, but includes parent directory navigation and returns full filename (with ext).

### Options
- `backfill <colour>` — background colour.
- `sort <name|rname|size|rsize|time|rtime>` — sort order.
- `talign <left|right|center>` — text alignment.

